ary-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249608/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"古巴高丁\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6a063561458ace44bce9ca2329377358/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_11_05_22.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        古巴高丁\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249609/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"吳京、謝霆鋒主演的《鏢人》在康城作推介。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57b7afd9426c5d62b4f726c99f7df2e6/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_11_05_23.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        吳京、謝霆鋒主演的《鏢人》在康城作推介。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249610/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"成龍與梁家輝主演的《捕風追影》都在康城登場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/351e0ee50781d49cd9ff0a3bcd8b3232/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_11_05_25_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        成龍與梁家輝主演的《捕風追影》都在康城登場。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249611/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"甄子丹昨出席「China Film 武傳四海功夫片出海論壇」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0b87b29d7d742501a0580cacc7a9d1b9/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_11_05_25.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甄子丹昨出席「China Film 武傳四海功夫片出海論壇」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249613/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"「中國之夜」在當地時間15日晚在康城舉行晚宴，作為「形象大使」的甄子丹將會亮相。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d78f90a4131efa5a4e9873e0b5701d4/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_11_05_26.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「中國之夜」在當地時間15日晚在康城舉行晚宴，作為「形象大使」的甄子丹將會亮相。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4249614/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"甄子丹帶同自導自演的《導火綫2》到康城宣傳。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7f68390d77cf2bc28f769ac7978b9a42/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_11_05_53.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甄子丹帶同自導自演的《導火綫2》到康城宣傳。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>謝霆鋒《怒火蔓延》與《鏢人》作影展推介</h2>\n<p>康城影展本月8日公布最終主競賽入圍名單，內地片《狂野时代》為最後一部入圍作品，亦成為今屆唯一一部爭金棕櫚的華語片。《狂》片由畢贛執導，易烊千璽、舒淇主演，今次是畢贛事隔多年重返康城，2018年他曾憑藉影片《地球最後的夜晚》入圍第71屆康城影展「一種關注」單元。\n\n</p>\n<p>此外，多部華語片將在康城影展作推介，其中包括：吳京 、謝霆鋒、李連杰、于適主演的《鏢人》；成龍、張子楓 、梁家輝主演的《捕風追影》，還有劉德華、謝霆鋒主演的《怒火蔓延》等。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
